OL,3,CDaughter refuses to pay bill for dad's
OL,4,Ccare as 'wasn't worth the money'
OL,6,FA woman is refusing to pay a bill
OL,7,Ftowards the cost of her father's
OL,8,FNorthumberland care home because of
OL,9,Fthe poor quality of care she claims he
OL,10,Freceived there.
OL,12,FLynne West's father lived at
OL,13,FNorthlands in Morpeth for six months
OL,14,Fbefore his death in early March.
OL,16,FLater last month, a report from the
OL,17,Fregulator, the Care Quality
OL,18,FCommission, rated the home as
OL,19,Finadequate following an inspection.
