OL,3,CDaughter refuses to pay bill for dad's
OL,4,Ccare as 'wasn't worth the money'
OL,6,FMs West says the release of that
OL,7,Freport has heightened her distress
OL,8,Fover her father, Don Johnston's time
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,F"Dad had dementia and also he used to
OL,12,Fwet a lot and he was always in a wet
OL,13,Fbed and wet boxer shorts and the food
OL,14,Fwas all over the floor and him," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FMs West explained: "It felt terrible
OL,18,Fbecause we'd placed Dad into a care
OL,19,Fhome to be cared for because we
OL,20,Fcouldn't do it at home."
