OL,6,FMr Johnston's family say they began to
OL,7,Fhave concerns about his care a number
OL,8,Fof weeks into his stay at Northlands.
OL,10,FThey have shared photographs which,
OL,11,Fthey say, reveal how stains and food
OL,12,Fwere left on and around him.
OL,14,FThey say another photograph shows a
OL,15,Ffacial injury which happened during
OL,16,Fone of two falls which resulted in
OL,17,Fvisits to hospital.
OL,19,FMr Johnston's death, on 3 March 2024,
OL,20,Fwas from natural causes.
