OL,3,CDaughter refuses to pay bill for dad's
OL,4,Ccare as 'wasn't worth the money'
OL,6,FDuring this time at Northlands, a
OL,7,Flarge proportion of his care was paid
OL,8,Ffor by Northumberland County Council.
OL,10,FHis family has now received a bill
OL,11,Ffrom the authority for just over
OL,12,F#3,700 to cover their contribution.
OL,14,FMs West has told ITV Tyne Tees that
OL,15,Fshe will not pay, on the grounds that
OL,16,Fher father's care "wasn't worth that
OL,17,Fmoney".
