OL,3,CDaughter refuses to pay bill for dad's
OL,4,Ccare as 'wasn't worth the money'
OL,6,FShe said: "I am hoping that other
OL,7,Fpeople that go into a care home do get
OL,8,Flooked after properly for the amount
OL,9,Fof money they are having to pay."
OL,11,F"It's too late for my dad now because
OL,12,Fhe passed away," she continued. "But I
OL,13,Fwant other people not to have to go
OL,14,Fthrough what I've had to go through."
OL,16,FNorthlands in Morpeth is run by
OL,17,FParkside Care, which, according to its
OL,18,Fwebsite, operates two other care homes
OL,19,Fin the North East.
