OL,6,F"Staff also tried using a pressure-
OL,7,Fsensor nurse call mat, but he would
OL,8,Ftry to step over or around this,
OL,9,Fcreating the greater risk of a fall
OL,10,Fdue to his condition."
OL,12,FIt is the lowest of four grades
OL,13,Favailable to the CQC.
OL,15,FThe inadequate rating puts the home
OL,16,Finto what are known as special
OL,17,Fmeasures, meaning it will be kept
OL,18,Funder review.
