OL,6,FAt the time of the CQC report,
OL,7,FParkside Care released a statement,
OL,8,Fsaying: "We regret that Northlands
OL,9,FCare Home has fallen below the
OL,10,Fstandards that we and the Care Quality
OL,11,FCommission expect.
OL,13,F"As noted in the report, we were in
OL,14,Fthe process of making improvements at
OL,15,Fthe time of the inspection in December
OL,16,Fand have recruited an experienced new
OL,17,FHead of Quality and Compliance.
