OL,6,F"They are working with colleagues on a
OL,7,Fcomprehensive plan to ensure that
OL,8,Fimprovements required to our record
OL,9,Fkeeping and procedures are made and
OL,10,Fsustained."
OL,12,FFollowing Ms West's decision to speak
OL,13,Fto ITV Tyne Tees, a spokesperson for
OL,14,FNorthumberland County Council said:
OL,15,F"We are aware of the CQC report, and
OL,16,Four Safeguarding, Commissioning and
OL,17,FCare Management teams will continue to
OL,18,Fwork with the home and the CQC to
OL,19,Fresolve the issues."
