OL,7,Ffortnight after Mr Johnston's funeral.
OL,9,FHis daughter Ms West says that as a
OL,10,Fresult, she and her family have not
OL,11,Fyet begun to grieve.
OL,13,FShe is though, determined to make a
OL,14,Fstand - in her view, for other
OL,15,Ffamilies experiencing similar issues.
